The Ibadan house of Mr. Sunday Igboho, a Yoruba activist who recently gave a quit notice to herdsmen in Ibarapa area of Oyo State, has been gutted by fire. It was gathered that the fire started in the early hours of Tuesday and destroyed the property located in Soka area of Ibadan. The cause of the inferno was unknown at the time of filing this report. Fire fighters deployed were able to quench the inferno after havoc had been wreaked on the property. See images <img src="https://i2.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/bd10ebb1-img-20210126-wa0023.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/533928e9-img-20210126-wa0024.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/b6d9a4da-img-20210126-wa0026.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i2.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/a681ef2f-img-20210126-wa0027.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i2.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/fd84659a-img-20210126-wa0029.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i0.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/c724f02d-img-20210126-wa0030.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/0c41ec09-img-20210126-wa0031.jpg?w=696&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" />